</li>
<li>
January 24, 2014, by Michael Wetter:<br/>
Revised implementation.
</li>
<li>
January 23, 2014, by Damien Picard:<br/>
First implementation.
</li>
</ul>
</html>"));
end internalResistancesOneUTube;
